code: @Override protected List<Status> doPoll() throws TwitterException {     Paging paging = getLastIdPaging().     log.trace("doPoll.getHomeTimeline(sinceId={})", paging.getSinceId()).     return getTwitter().getHomeTimeline(paging). }
@Override protected List<Status> doDirect() throws TwitterException {     log.trace("doDirect.getHomeTimeline()").     return getTwitter().getHomeTimeline(). }
